data.description: Assumable FHA Loan at 3.625% & Easy to Show!   Welcome to this tailor-made Two-story abode tucked away in the heart of the Woodmont community, No HOA. Situated just moments from Foley schools, the nearby hospital, and the pristine beaches of Gulf Shores, this home stands as an epitome of comfort and luxury on its expansive exterior lot.  Step inside to be greeted by exquisite engineered hardwood floors, soaring vaulted ceilings, handpicked light fixtures, and an inviting wood-burning fireplace. The state-of-the-art kitchen is a chef's delight with its polished granite countertops and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances.  The primary suite on the ground floor promises serenity with its tray ceilings, expansive walk-in closet, and a luxurious bathroom complete with a garden tub and a standalone shower. The upper level houses three generously-sized bedrooms and a well-appointed bathroom.  Outside, a spacious backyard beckons with its ideal patio setup, perfect for those alfresco gatherings. A surrounding privacy fence guarantees seclusion, while strategically placed gutters efficiently manage rainfall. The addition of a double garage ensures ease of parking and storage.  Positioned conveniently near Tanger's shopping haven and the exhilarating OWA Amusement park, this residence is a fusion of prime location and impeccable taste. Moreover, it holds promising potential for Airbnb investment. Awaiting its next owner, this home is a blend of warmth and modern elegance.
